title: Random FTB
description: May be placed on any Bunny which must feed the amounts rolled by the end of its next turn or die.

title: Very Large Prune Danish
description: May be used once by a player to feed any (or all) bunnies in the Bunny Circle any amounts of Cabbage and Water.

title: Everyone Feed a Bunny
description: May be given to all opponents with a Bunny. Each must feed any one bunny the amounts shown by the end of their next turns their bunny dies.

title: Giza Plateau (#4)
description: The player who picks the last Mysterious Place card controls all cards played that have a Yellow Bal with a Red Stripe.
